title: New Frontier (Dark Horse - 1992) (Rumor-Novus-HD)  Cherkas
description:
Written by Michael Cherkas and John Sabljic. Art and cover by Michael Cherkas. The '60s were filled with memorable events: the H-Bombing of Pyongyang, the assassination of Bert Parks, and Fidel Castro's World Series no-hitter. There was no event, however, that etched itself into the public memory as did the death of the most glamorous and popular movie star in history, Rubi Fields. Now, 30 years later, her death plays a role in a baffling murder... or does it?


Special Thanks to Zoddy for the issues
